sparqlQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT  ?uri
WHERE
  { ?uri   a                     <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Country> .
    ?cave  a                     <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Cave>
      { ?cave  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location>  ?uri }
    UNION
      { ?cave  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location>  ?loc .
        ?loc   <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country>  ?uri
      }
  }
GROUP BY ?uri
HAVING ( COUNT(?cave) > 10 )
